column2: SB Plays Beacon Pines 01 - Adorable But Worrying
column7:
That is both my favorite kind of adorable AND my favorite kind of worrying!

Beacon Pines is a beautiful little storybook adventure about some almost unreasonably cute kids having a very fun and idyllic summer vacation in which nothing truly horrifying happens to any of them at all almost! Can we find the words to tell a version of this story that doesn't end in a total nightmare?
